chr2	15708677	16185337	2p24.3 MYCN-DDX1 duplication region	gain	2p24.3 MYCN-DDX1 duplication region is associated with Duplications encompassing MYCN and DDX1 predispose to neuroblastoma and may modify tumor progression and treatment response. Key genes: MYCN; DDX1. Care usually involves developmental and educational support, regular health checks for organ involvement, and management of seizures or growth concerns where relevant. The presentation and severity can vary widely, even among individuals with the same deletion. (OMIM: 164840)
